summary:
My life has been dedicated to creating co-learning and collaborative environments for young leaders to reflect on themselves and their role in this fast changing world. A world that is in need of innovative answers, collaborative solutions and transformative work.

As a program developer and facilitator I specialize in mindfulness, Theory U, emotional intelligence, leadership and community building.

As an anthropologist I gained excellent observation skills, understanding of group dynamics and ease with with the complexity of reality.

Organizing international events has made me a skilled and hands-on team player.
